  "title": "AB03 - Preschool Principal | Preschool Teacher | Infant & Toddler Educator",
  "description": "<p><strong>Available Positions & Salary Range</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Principal</strong>: $5,000 – $7,000</p><p><strong>Vice Principal</strong>: $4,500 – $5,000</p><p><strong>English / Malay / Chinese Language Teacher</strong>: $3,600 – $4,600</p><p><strong>Infant Care Teacher</strong>: $2,800 – $3,600</p><p><strong>Assistant Teacher</strong>: $2,200 – $2,500<br /><br /><strong>Working Conditions</strong></p><ul><li><p>5-day work week (Monday to Friday)</p></li><li><p>Islandwide deployment (assigned to centres near your residence where possible)</p></li></ul></li></ul><h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Plan and deliver English, Malay, or Chinese language lessons in accordance with the organisation’s curriculum framework</p></li><li><p>Design and implement developmentally appropriate programmes for young children</p></li><li><p>Ensure the safety, health, and well-being of children at all times</p></li><li><p>Engage children through meaningful learning activities to enhance their development</p></li><li><p>Observe, assess, and document children’s learning progress, behaviour, social development, and physical health</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Diploma or Degree in Early Childhood Care & Education, <strong>or</strong></p></li><li><p>ECDA certification (L1 / L2 / EY1 / EY2 / LON), <strong>or</strong></p></li><li><p>Relevant experience in early childhood education</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Benefits</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Competitive salary package</p></li><li><p>Career progression opportunities</p></li><li><p>Supportive and professional working environment<br /></p><p><strong>If you are keen to apply, please send me your resume and job applied for on WhatsApp at 8093 8699 or email me at anabel.thesupreme@gmail.com (˶ᵔ ᵕ ᵔ˶)</strong></p><p>❄️Anabel Boon Xue Qi | Consultant Associate (R25159272) |📍The Supreme HR Advisory EA No: 14C7279</p></li></ul>",
